race.description: Wollongong First Aid Midway Mdn Handicap
race.comment: ROSE OF FENWAY (6) returned from a let-up at start two, when a gritty on-pace second over 1100m at Hawkesbury in fast time. Only has to hold that form to shed her Maiden status with Alysha Collett retaining the ride. BRUTAL ADVANCE (1) is holding his form at this level and closed off strongly when fourth over 1100m at Hawkesbury. Gets in light with the 3kg claim and likely to roll forward from the sticky draw. Leading prospect. VINGT NEUF NOIR (8) made an even return in town when a plugging seventh over 1100m at Canterbury. Will derive great benefit from that outing and relish the extra trip. Each-way. KOSRAE (10) even debut when found the line late to finish fourth over 1100m at Nowra. Strips fitter and will appreciate the extra ground.
